about_me.des:
Forensic Investigator with a demonstrated history of working in the computer industry. Skilled in Java and Python,
with a Bachelor’s Degree focused in Computer Engineering from Çukurova Üniversitesi.

projects.forensafe: Forensafe is a computer and mobile forensics tool used by investigators in digital crime and fraud cases.
projects.signLanguageTranslationSoftware: An application that aimed to help deaf people which analizes the sign a deaf person make and convert it into speaken language, Developed using C# for back-end and windows forms for front-end.
projects.keybusiness: A web ERP project that was built using Java Spring-Boot , Hibernate , MySQL database and Angular 4 on the frontend.
